articles.title: NASA details plan to build a levitating robot train on the moon - Space.com
articles.description: NASA's plan to build a train track on the moon is part of the agency's Innovative Advanced Concepts program, which aims to develop "science fiction-like" projects for future space exploration.
articles.content:
